Name: Dungeon Maze
About the game: You find yourself in a maze, dark and eerily quiet. You're trapped. Gather enough coins, and you might be able to get out. Thing is, you're not the only one trapped inside. Is something breathing behind you? Quick info: Objective: Find all the coins, escape the maze Locomotion: Teleporting Maze: Random each time Size: Not too big, quick-ish to play. You can get lost though. Monster: Scary
